FOR C++:TO RUN SERVER:  g++ -o server1 server1.cpp -lpthread
                ./server1 8080    // ANY PORT NUMBER WORKS

FOR CLIENT: g++ -o client1 client1.c
            ./client localhost 8080

FOR C:TO RUN SERVER:  gcc -o server server.c -lpthread
                ./server 8080    // ANY PORT NUMBER WORKS

FOR CLIENT: gcc -o client client.c
            ./client localhost 8080
